## Self-Healing Recovery Module

```python
from desktop_automation_agent import (
    ScreenCheckType,
    ScreenVerificationCheck,
    SelfHealingRecoveryModule,
    SelfHealingRecoveryRequest,
)

recovery = SelfHealingRecoveryModule(
    classifier=error_classifier,
    verifier=screen_verifier,
    screenshot_backend=screenshot_backend,
    input_runner=input_simulator,
    refresh_callback=lambda: window_manager.focus_window(title="Chat App"),
    reauthenticate_callback=reauthenticate_session,
    dismiss_dialog_callback=dismiss_dialogs,
)

result = recovery.recover(
    SelfHealingRecoveryRequest(
        error=RuntimeError("Application not responding"),
        target_checks=[
            ScreenVerificationCheck(
                check_id="ready",
                check_type=ScreenCheckType.TEXT_PRESENT,
                target_text="Message",
            )
        ],
    ),
    retry_step=lambda: sequencer.replay_step(failed_step),
)
```

